sync" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Olivia-Rodrigo-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Olivia-Rodrigo-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Olivia-Rodrigo-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Olivia-Rodrigo-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Olivia-Rodrigo-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Olivia-Rodrigo-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple">Apple</a>发布了 iPhone 15 Pro，并发布了一段用手机拍摄的奥利维亚·<a href="/artists/olivia-rodrigo">罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo</a> ) 歌曲《Get Him Back》的音乐视频。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/olivia-rodrigo-guts-album-review-vampire-3493907">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) – 《胆量》评论：流行音乐的轰动确保了她作为一代天才的地位</a></strong></li></ul><p>《让他回来》的音乐视频由 Jack Begert 执导，与 Apple 合作使用 iPhone 15 Pro 拍摄，展示了多个罗德里戈走来走去、毁坏公寓的场景，以及她在车窗爆炸的街道上行走的场景。</p><p>它还由刘晓“X”进行摄影指导，他在 15 Pro 的 5 倍长焦相机上使用了“崩溃变焦技术”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="奥利维亚罗德里戈 - 让他回来！ （官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZsJ-BHohXRI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这位流行歌手在 Apple Music 1 上向 Zane Lowe 谈到这首歌时说道：“我们写了一首我不喜欢的歌曲，我彻底崩溃了。我当时想，‘天哪，我不会写歌。我在这方面太差劲了无论如何，我不想变得非常消极。”</p><p>她继续说道：“然后我们休息了一会儿，回来写了《让他回来》，这是我最喜欢的歌曲之一。所以我只是想告诉你，永远不要放弃。是啊，写起来超级有趣。我真的很喜欢合唱。它对我来说很粘，感觉就像是我想让一群人唱的东西。”</p><p> <em>NME</em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/olivia-rodrigo-guts-album-review-vampire-3493907">在对她的第二张唱片《Guts》进行五星级评论时</a>表示：“《Guts》不仅在音乐意义上具有过渡性。这标志着罗德里戈青少年时期的结束，这一时刻具有重大意义，因为她最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-announces-second-album-guts-3461767">在一份声明中</a>表示，她感觉自己在 18 岁到 20 岁之间成长了“10 岁”。在这里，她进行了直率的自我分析，同时反思更广泛的文化观念，即表现和吞咽愤怒，以满足他人的愿望和需要。它展示了真正的力量、范围和多功能性——所有这些都是罗德里戈所拥有的。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxGkzAqLwtH/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67