ds/2023/09/animal-collective-live-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/animal-collective-live-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/animal-collective-live-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/animal-collective">Animal Collective</a>宣布了将于本月晚些时候发行的新专辑的详细信息。请在下面获取有关“现在不是”的所有详细信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/animal-collective-time-skiffs-review-3154040">动物集体 - “时间小船”评论：冒险家重回正轨</a></strong></li></ul><p>这张专辑是继去年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/animal-collective-time-skiffs-review-3154040">《Time Skiffs》</a>之后，乐队在 2023 年为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/caroline-polachek-has-been-working-on-a-song-for-a-new-a24-film-3398570">A24 电影</a><em>《The Inspection》</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/animal-collective-soundtrack-upcoming-film-the-inspection-share-new-song-crucible-3345267">录制了原声带</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/animal-collective-are-reissuing-debut-album-new-ep-3412544">重新发行了他们的首张专辑和 EP</a> 。</p><p> 《It isn&#39;t Now》将于 9 月 29 日通过 Domino 发行，乐队将在发行前举办特别的聆听派对。</p><p>聆听第一首单曲“Gem &amp; I”，并查看下面的聆听方详细信息。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="动物集体 - 宝石与我（官方音频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/x7JAxWHnYlM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3498192" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IsntItNowListeningPart_all_square.jpg" alt="动物集体" width="1080" height="1080" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IsntItNowListeningPart_all_square.jpg 1080w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IsntItNowListeningPart_all_square-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IsntItNowListeningPart_all_square-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IsntItNowListeningPart_all_square-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IsntItNowListeningPart_all_square-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IsntItNowListeningPart_all_square-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p><p>在对《Time Skiffs》的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/animal-collective-time-skiffs-review-3154040">四星评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>表示，乐队的新专辑让他们在几张唱片“如此混乱以至于令人遗憾地在混乱中迷失”之后再次找到了立足点。</p><p>去年，乐队还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/animal-collective-have-cancelled-their-uk-european-tour-dates-3326104">取消了计划中的英国和欧洲</a>巡演，以支持原定在爱尔兰拉开帷幕的“Time Skiffs”，并在一份声明中表示，在计划巡演时，他们面临着“经济现实不起作用，也不可持续”。</p><p> “从通货膨胀到货币贬值，再到臃肿的运输和运输成本等等，我们根本无法为这次旅行制定一个即使一切进展顺利也不会亏损的预算，”他们继续说道。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/animal-collective-announce-new-album-it-isnt-now-and-detail-listening-parties-3498185">Animal Collective 宣布新专辑《It isn&#39;t Now》后，详细聆听派对</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
