eight="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Blur-R.E.M.-Garbage-Idlewild-and-more-set-for-special-90s-reissues-for-National-Album-Day.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="全国专辑日" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Blur-R.E.M.-Garbage-Idlewild-and-more-set-for-special-90s-reissues-for-National-Album-Day.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Blur-R.E.M.-Garbage-Idlewild-and-more-set-for-special-90s-reissues-for-National-Album-Day-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Blur-R.E.M.-Garbage-Idlewild-and-more-set-for-special-90s-reissues-for-National-Album-Day-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Blur-R.E.M.-Garbage-Idlewild-and-more-set-for-special-90s-reissues-for-National-Album-Day-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Blur-R.E.M.-Garbage-Idlewild-and-more-set-for-special-90s-reissues-for-National-Album-Day-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Blur-R.E.M.-Garbage-Idlewild-and-more-set-for-special-90s-reissues-for-National-Album-Day-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">Blur</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/r-e-m">REM</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/garbage">Garbage</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idlewild">Idlewild</a>等乐队将在下个月的全国专辑日重新发行 1990 年代的专辑。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/rem-best-albums-michael-stipe-monster-automatic-for-the-people-2638853">REM：每张专辑的排名和评级</a></strong></li></ul><p>正如<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/national-album-day-2023-to-pay-homage-1990s-albums-3413258">今年早些时候宣布的</a>那样，全国专辑日将于 10 月 14 日举行，并特别聚焦 90 年代。</p><p>其他将于当天重新发行唱片的艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fatboy-slim">Fatboy Slim</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-dylan">Bob Dylan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wu-tang-clan">Wu-Tang Clan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeff-buckley">Jeff Buckley</a>等。</p><p>今年是该活动的第六届—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-first-ever-national-album-day-has-been-announced-2358072">最初于 2018 年启动</a>——旨在让人们了解定义 20 年代的艺术家和专辑。该活动还将庆祝 LP 专辑问世 75 周年。</p><p>请参阅下面重新发行的专辑的完整列表。</p><p> <strong>808 状态 –</strong> &#39;ex:el&#39; <em>(2LP)</em><br /> <strong>Ace Of Base –</strong> &#39;Happy Nation&#39; <em>（乙烯基图片光盘）</em><br /> <strong>Babybird –</strong> “丑陋的美丽” <em>(2LP)</em><br /><strong>贝琳达·卡莱尔 –</strong> “自由地生活” <em>（乙烯基图片光盘）</em><br /> <strong>Blur –</strong> “现代生活是垃圾” <em>（2LP 透明橙色乙烯基）</em><br /><strong>鲍勃·迪伦 –</strong> 《Time Out Of Mind》 <em>（2LP 透明金胶唱片）</em><br /> <strong>Catatonia –</strong> “国际天鹅绒” <em>（1LP 再生彩色乙烯基）</em><br /> <strong>Dannii –</strong> 《女孩》 <em>（2XLP / 4CD 盒装）</em><br /> <strong>Dinosaur Jr.</strong> – &#39;Where You Been&#39; <em>（限量版双溅乙烯基）</em><br /> <strong>Duster –</strong> “Stratosphere”（25 周年纪念版） <em>（1LP 透明和黑色泼溅乙烯基）</em><br /><strong>永恒 –</strong> “永远” <em>（1LP 再生彩色乙烯基）</em><br /> <strong>Fatboy Slim –</strong> &#39;You&#39;ve Come A Long Way Baby&#39; <em>（2LP 半速重制版）</em><br /><strong>加布里埃尔 –</strong> &#39;崛起&#39; <em>(1LP)</em><br /><strong>垃圾 –</strong> “2.0 版” <em>（2LP 蓝色乙烯基）</em><br /> <strong>Ginuwine –</strong> “单身汉” <em>（2LP 红色乙烯基）</em><br /> <strong>Hole –</strong> &#39;Live Through This&#39; (1LP)<br /> <strong>Idlewild –</strong> “Captain” <em>（1LP 再生彩色乙烯基）</em><br /><strong>詹姆斯 –</strong> &#39;Laid&#39; (2LP)<br /><strong>詹姆斯 –</strong> “黄金妈妈” (2LP)<br /> <strong>Jeff Buckley –</strong> &#39;Grace&#39; <em>（1LP 丁香酒乙烯基）</em><br /> <strong>Leftfield –</strong> “左派” <em>（2LP 白色和黑色大理石纹乙烯基）</em><br /><strong>灯塔家族——</strong> “海洋大道”<br /><strong>马克·阿尔蒙德 –</strong> 《公寓交响曲》 <em>（2LP / 豪华版 6CD/DVD）</em><br /><strong>梅兰妮·C –</strong> 《北极星》 <em>(1LP)</em><br /> <strong>Nas –</strong> &#39;It Was Written&#39; <em>（2LP 金色和黑色乙烯基）</em><br /> <strong>Neneh Cherry –</strong> &#39;Man&#39; <em